summary: in case you weren’t aware, on friday, i got to experience the reputation stadium tour for myself. to say i enjoyed it would be...
caption: in case you weren’t aware, on friday, i got to experience the reputation stadium tour for myself. to say i enjoyed it would be an understatement. i got to watch someone i’ve stood by for twelve years absolutely kill it in front of 80,000 people on the three year anniversary of when i saw you last. the whole stadium was there for the same reason: to listen to stories of a girl and to be so unapologetically happy about it. i’m so lucky i got to witness not only you sing about your life and how people have taken you down and how you have clawed your way out of that, but a show made up of lessons to take away. i got to sing back lyrics that mean something to me, watch you be amazed by the ovation we gave before you could even begin singing new year’s day and have the surprise of niall horan coming to duet slow hands. at least i did one thing right by standing by your side for as long and i will continue to do so until i’m blue in the face. i will hold onto these memories, i will stay @taylorswift @taylornation.
